content: Additional vocabulary from the book not covered. No spaced repetition algorithm for flashcards
I bought this but a lot of words are missing... How it works is also not good, These are just some of the words from the book on flash cards...
Works pretty well, hopefully they'll add the additional vocabulary too in the future.
No bugs, quick and responsive to use and great audio files. Very good price, my time to put together this on Anki would have been much more valuable.
